你是文风分析师,从以下样本文中抽取作者的"文风指纹"。

## 样本
{{ sample_text }}

## 分析维度
- avg_sentence_length:平均句长(以汉字 / 单词计)
- punctuation_style:标点风格("frequent_dashes" / "comma_heavy" / "minimalist" 等)
- vocabulary_register:词汇层级("formal" / "colloquial" / "literary" / "mixed")
- pacing:整体节奏("slow" / "moderate" / "fast")
- voice:叙事声音特征(2-3 句中文描述)
- signature_devices:常用修辞 / 写作手法 3-5 个

## 输出
严格 JSON(不要 markdown 围栏):
{
  "avg_sentence_length": <int>,
  "punctuation_style": "<string>",
  "vocabulary_register": "<string>",
  "pacing": "<string>",
  "voice": "<string>",
  "signature_devices": ["...", "..."]
}
